race.description: Fred Vella Tyre & Crash Repair Handicap
race.comment: PRICILLA'S CHOICE (4) was back to her best last time at Oakbank when destroying her rivals over this trip. Carries the big weight but is drawn well and can double the dose. GRUELLING (3) improved sharply second-up when making light work of them at Bordertown. Strips fitter and has more to offer. SPIRIT OF FLIGHT (13) is knocking on the door and should be peaking now. LUCKY FORTUNA (12) scored two back at this track but was below her best last time. Backs up quickly and will appreciate returning to this venue. Expect her to give a great sight in front. ROYAL FOX (1) warmed nicely late last start to finish just shy of the frame at headquarters. Backs up quickly and gets an important claim. Don't take lightly. ANDREW'S MEMORY (5) chased in vain behind PRICILLA'S CHOICE at the latest but doesn't need to improve much to turn the tables. Have to include.
